{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-8433bf9217c02ed8", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# XTTS: a Massively Multilingual Zero-Shot Text-to-Speech Model\narXiv: 2406.04904\nAuthors: Edresson Casanova, Kelly Davis, Eren Gölge, Görkem Göknar, Iulian Gulea, Logan Hart, Aya Aljafari, Joshua Meyer, Reuben Morais, Samuel Olayemi, Julian Weber\nYear: 2024 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. We introduced XyzTTS a new multilingual ZS-TTS model that achieves SOTA results in 16 languages.\n  2. XyzTTS is the first massively multilingual ZS-TTS model, supporting low/medium resource languages.\n  3. Our model can perform cross-language ZS-TTS without needing a parallel training dataset.\n  4. XyzTTS model and checkpoints are publicly available on GitHub and Hugging Face repositories.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-AR-LLM, TTS/控制-参考语音, TTS/功能-多语言, TTS/功能-多说话人", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "98a9a38b-97c4-4f62-9652-7dd7b7ca3c40", "uuid": "8bd0bb3b-59d2-4432-9ac8-3ff00f23bd5e", "timestamp": "2026-07-24T07:08:32.826Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# XTTS: a Massively Multilingual Zero-Shot Text-to-Speech Model\narXiv: 2406.04904\nAuthors: Edresson Casanova, Kelly Davis, Eren Gölge, Görkem Göknar, Iulian Gulea, Logan Hart, Aya Aljafari, Joshua Meyer, Reuben Morais, Samuel Olayemi, Julian Weber\nYear: 2024 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. We introduced XyzTTS a new multilingual ZS-TTS model that achieves SOTA results in 16 languages.\n  2. XyzTTS is the first massively multilingual ZS-TTS model, supporting low/medium resource languages.\n  3. Our model can perform cross-language ZS-TTS without needing a parallel training dataset.\n  4. XyzTTS model and checkpoints are publicly available on GitHub and Hugging Face repositories.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-AR-LLM, TTS/控制-参考语音, TTS/功能-多语言, TTS/功能-多说话人", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false